# Scenario 3: Corner Case & Precision Test (All Combinations)

## Test Information

- **Description**: Testing all 9 combinations of zero/max/min values
- **Test 1**: zero × zero → 0 (0x00000)
- **Test 2**: zero × max → 0 (0x00000)
- **Test 3**: zero × min → 0 (0x00000)
- **Test 4**: max × zero → 0 (0x00000)
- **Test 5**: max × max → 258064 (0x3f010)
- **Test 6**: max × min → -260096 (0xc0800)
- **Test 7**: min × zero → 0 (0x00000)
- **Test 8**: min × max → -260096 (0xc0800)
- **Test 9**: min × min → 262144 (0x40000)

---
